          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; padding-bottom: 6px">
           <strong>üá¨üá™ Georgia - EU ministers concerned.</strong> European FMs issued a joint statement expressing deep concern over the arrests of opposition figures and journalists. The statement condemned the Georgian Dream party‚Äôs authoritarian shift and called for the release of political prisoners. It warned that recent developments have strained EU-Georgia ties and jeopardized Georgia‚Äôs EU candidacy (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-jul-25-worldwide-11-eu-georgia-rift?source=website" target="_blank">EU Georgia rift</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; padding-bottom: 6px">
           <strong>üáµüá∏ Palestine - American killed.</strong> The family of Sayfollah Musallet, a 20-year-old Palestinian-American beaten to death by Israeli settlers, is urging the US to launch an independent investigation. Rights groups condemn Washington‚Äôs silence and called for accountability. Critics say the US lacks the political will to protect Palestinian-Americans (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-jul-25-worldwide-12-push-for-accountability?source=website" target="_blank">push for accountability</a>).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; padding-bottom: 6px">
           <strong>üá™üá∏ Spain - Clashes with far right and migrants.</strong> Torre Pacheco, a town in southern Spain, saw a second night of violence after far-right protests over migrant arrivals escalated. The unrest began after an elderly man was allegedly assaulted by North African youths, sparking threats and attacks against migrants. Five people were injured, and one was arrested (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-14-jul-25-worldwide-13-spanish-political-tension?source=website" target="_blank">Spanish political tension</a>). 
